        Sorry, but you are not only Pissed Off Plenty, you're Tunnel Vision Plenty.  I am truly amazed at your abilty to read all kinds of stupid shit into what I've posted.  Sorry for the name calling, but you've got NO right to pervert (twist) what I've written so that it fits YOUR warped perception of me and/or my thoughts.  <br>
        How come e-v-e-r-y time someone posts on these many, many pages that they did not serve in Vietnam they are immediately ripped by Vietnam Vets?  Are VVets the only ones qualified to speak about the war, have feelings about the war, discuss the war, etc.?  When did VVets acquire a monopoly on this?  I mean, none of us served in the American Civil War, but I think we can all agree it was a human tragedy of the highest order.  <br>
        As for Vietnam, does anyone with an IQ over 70 NOT blame our leaders for leading us into THAT tragedy? <br>
